data.description: Fantastic curb appeal with this single level living home that has many updates creating a warm and inviting feel. Full of natural light, many windows have been updated and recently painted. Spacious and functional floor plan. Updates include: 2020 furnace, several updated windows/blinds, fiber optic internet available, in last 10 years roof, A/C, & bathroom. Enjoy your evenings under the covered patio, surrounded by mature trees. Fully fenced yard, RV parking, sought after location because of the convenience to schools, parks, shopping, etc.
